<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>

<body>
Dear <%= @email_property[:contact_name] %>,
<p>
  Thank you for submitting order <%= @email_property[:order_code]%> via GoodCity.
</p>
<h4>
  Please provide detailed address information.
</h4>
<p>
  Please reply to this email and provide detailed address information for where the items need to be delivered. We cannot process the order further until we receive this.
</p>
<h4>
  Confirmation email
</h4>
<p>
  After receiving address information our team will start reviewing the order and will contact you if they have further questions. You will receive another email when the order is confirmed. We apologize if some of the requested items are unavailable or if we cannot confirm your preferred time-slots due to limited volunteer manpower.
</p>
<p>
  Need to reschedule or modify your ? Log in at <a href="https://<%= @email_property[:domain]%>.goodcity.hk">https://<%= @email_property[:domain]%>.goodcity.hk</a> and click on “dashboard” to access or modify your records.
</p>
<p>
  Please feel free to reply to this message if you have further enquiries. <br/><br/>
  We look forward to assisting in any way we can! <br/><br/>
  Yours sincerely,
  Hong Kong Distribution Office<br/>
  Crossroads Foundation<br/>
  Office Tel: 2272 9343<br/>
  Email: local@crossroads.org.hk
</p>
</body>
</html>
